{
  "stem": "13981.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Whether he had remorse over what had happened, I'm in no position to say.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in the movie that-- in the documentary that-- we talked a lot about Hitler.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one day, I asked him, you know, it had been rumored that Hitler's sex life was not of the normal kind.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A lot of people had heard about it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so one day I asked him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he told me that Eva Braun had told him that they had oral sex.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now Eva Braun used to be Hoffmann's employee.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She worked in his photo lab.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one day Hitler walked in, and he said to Hoffmann, who's that lady over there?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And Hoffman introduced them to each other.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] she became his mistress.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And until a few hours before their death was his mistress, until they were actually married.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] but her married name didn't last but about two hours.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not, not much really.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because-- he just told me that he introduced them and--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To get into the courtroom incriminating evidence pictures, like the atrocities that you have seen and you-- and also, for instance, it was-- it so happened we had the lamp shades that Ilse Koch, of-- who was the commander of Buchenwald camp, had made of human skins.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When she saw some better than average looking guys come in, she had them separated right away, had shot them-- had them shot, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] had them skinned, then had the skins tanned.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of these, then leather, she had made lamp shades.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I myself carried two of these lamp shades into the courtroom.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was-- and also, we had to produce organizational charts, anything that you could look at and use as evidence.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
